# SCHEDULE PROPOSED BY VUONG (Jan 12)
1. Design a banner with the domain name on it (fitheart.org for example) and the pictures of related products.
No need of logo.
I will do this with Inkscape in vector graphic format (I used it frequently).
Then you modify if needed.
2. Choose domain.
Normally I search on Godaddy.com to see the price.
I am currently investigating how to choose wisely on blackhatworld.com.
Frankly, I am not so interested in the domain fitheart since I am not sure if someone really search on google such a keyword.
Not sure if we need hosting or not.
3. Choose three product groups (within two-three days).
You will choose two groups and so do I (within medical supplies / equipments niche).
After that, we select three groups.
This does not mean that we choose your two groups and my one group, for example.
We can choose your two groups and another group which is suitable.
4. Continue to fix the website.
But do not focus on it as we are going to improve it all the time.
Indeed, I suppose the index page should only has one overview article where we presents the product groups and list the reviews (like thebestespressomachines.org)
Your opinion is welcome.
Good work !!!


